OL,5,CBritton
OL,7,FA 63-year-old man from Hampshire has
OL,8,Fbeen given a 10-year restraining order
OL,9,Ffor stalking TV presenter Fern Britton
OL,10,Fby sending her flowers and staying in
OL,11,Fthe cottage that she rented out in
OL,12,FCornwall.
OL,14,FJames Haviland, of Great Oaks Chase,
OL,15,FChineham, pleaded guilty to stalking
OL,16,Fthe former ITV This Morning star
OL,17,Fwithout causing fear, alarm or
OL,18,Fdistress, between November 20, 2021
OL,19,Fand September 16, 2023, in the
OL,20,FWadebridge area.
