OL,16,Fcommunity order which requires him to
OL,17,Fcomplete 12 rehabilitation sessions
OL,18,Fand 150 hours of unpaid work ` and he
OL,19,Fwas told to pay a #114 victim
OL,20,Fsurcharge and #85 court costs.
